{"tid":1524440,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［攻擊黨鐵，正式啟動］政權爪牙皆敵人，差佬係，從此黨鐵亦如是","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T14:49:30.000Z","uid":149630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1153a930e02f2af4790d835a9540e7f29925dbf0","tid":1524440,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:15:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黨鐵係政權鬼卒<br />\n人所皆知<br />\n但顧忌佢游擊運輸功能<br />\n對黨鐵敵意一直留有一綫</span></span><br />\n二零一九年八月三十一晚<br />\n黨鐵將荃灣線、觀塘線、港島線、將軍澳線等列車停駛<br />\n更任由差佬入內中出<br />\n無差別恐怖襲擊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">繼元朗黑社會後<br />\n差佬接力<br />\n與黨鐵合演殘殺香港人嘅鬧劇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黨鐵游擊戰失去角色<br />\n終於露出猙獰妖相<br />\n正式與香港人為敵</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當黨鐵游擊功能報廢<br />\n我方亦再無包袱<br />\n不再顧忌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攻擊黨鐵，就係攻擊政權</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">若然未報<br />\n時辰未到<br />\n<br />\n罪孽深重<br />\n係時候報</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZfRi1Ji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZfRi1Ji.jpg&h=f664177c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lfbu8oi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLfbu8oi.jpg&h=eca2ec88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTVS57M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTVS57M.jpg&h=fcf1c39c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e91b1e0a0d1487fffa4cbef50c5928fd4ba457e6","tid":1524440,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:15:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e1cfa0bfed0dbeb361db9841d7f5f36184dcb7c","tid":1524440,"uid":149630,"like":0,"di